## Endpoints

### GET /api/v1/

This endpoint is used to check if the API is running.

#### Response

```json
{
    ""message"": ""Welcome to the API""
}
```

### POST /api/v1/register

This endpoint is used to register a new user.

#### Request

```json
{
    ""username"": ""username"",
    ""password"": ""password""
}
```

#### Response

```json
{
    ""message"": ""User registered successfully""
}
```

### POST /api/v1/login

This endpoint is used to login a user.

#### Request

```json
{
    ""username"": ""username"",
    ""password"": ""password""
}
```

#### Response

```json
{
    ""message"": ""User logged in successfully"",
    ""token"": ""token""
}
```

This endpoint is used to get a list of all users.

[

        ""username"": ""username""
    },
    {
        ""id"": 2,

Abstract This study aims to determine the effect of the application of the cooperative learning model type of think pair share (TPS) on the learning outcomes of students in the material of the structure of the atom This research is a quasi-experimental research with a non-equivalent control group design The population in this study were all students of class X MIPA 1 SMA Negeri 1 Kota Tegal in the academic year 2018 2019 The sample in this study were two classes namely class X MIPA 1 as an experimental class and class X MIPA 2 as a control class The sampling technique used was purposive sampling The data collection technique used was a test The data analysis technique used was the t-test The results of the study showed that the average value of the experimental class was higher than the control class namely 78.75 and 73.75 The results of the t-test obtained tcount> ttable (2.9> 1.67) and the significance value (0.007 <0.05) This means that there is an effect of the application of the cooperative learning model type of think pair share (TPS) on the learning outcomes of students in the material of the structure of the atom
